node.text: Video dedicated for my baby girl Wolfie, I hope you will enjoy watching it when you get older so you can remember & relive those amazing moments we had together (everytime i think of the fact babies forget when they’re babies as they grow it makes me cry cause I cannot believe those moments are soooo intense for me but she won’t remember🥺) hope this video will help hihi ❤️ As you can see, you were always the most intelligent, beautiful & incredible girl, you certainly still are today (yes talking to you Wolfie of the future haha) You make everyday the most beautiful day of my life again & again & again. You have this super power of bringing everyone together & making everyone smile on a daily basis 💕 i love you mi amor , the most loved baby on the planet 🍉

node.text: I know it's not made to be vertical but I just found this video, who remember ? ❤️ missing you @jonathan_germain ☀️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Elisabeth Rioux 👙 on September 19, 2021 tagging @hoaka_swimwear. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
That morning I felt like the pope on my balcony, except i’m just that instagram girl taking herself way too seriously.. well hi everyone downstairs 🥲
I’m currently in bed, just about to go to sleep & i cannot believe tomorrow will be the last time I wake up in Spain 🥺 we’ve been here for 2 weeks now, much longer than we planned because we loved it so much 🇪🇸 My favorite plan when I travel is definitely: no plan ! Every night we’d talk about what would would do the next day, “do we want to stay an extra night ?” “Do we want to try this city tomorrow ?” “Do we feel like a more historical city tomorrow or a beach vibe ?” , it’s just super exciting & stress free cause you have no expectations except for the next day 🌈 All we had planned before coming here was our flight to come & our flight back home (which we moved haha) , now our way home is in 10 days, tomorrow we’ll just get to the airport & be like “hey what do you have as an option for us ? ” & we’ll go there (as long as there is beaches & coffee i’ll be happy 🥲😋) if you have any recommendations in Europe I’m still happy  to hear & consider them 🌹 tomorrow is THE day ✈️

node.text:
Maybe not the most “instagrammable photos” but clearly my fav day since we got here , I always loved trying new things in my life, I am always seeking to see new stuff, go to new places, try new sports but since I’m with Wolfie it’s like eveeeerything is new, we did bicycles & it felt like it was the first time in my life… i don’t know how to explain it but when I have Wolfie trying new things it’s like all new for me too ?! I feel the same excitement but I live it through her eyes 🥰 (i’m not clear but I’m also not able to put words on this feeling, please tell me i’m not the only one to feel that haha) 
I love my very special & not normal beautiful family 💕

node.text: It all started this week when someone told me I should stop breastfeeding Wolfie because she’s “too old”, I posted a lazy photo with a bun wearing a comfy outfit & breastfeeding with a caption just to educate people & try to normalize breastfeeding but Instagram didn’t like it, it was deleted.. it’s like I was slap in the face twice this week.. why are we trying to shut down one of the most beautiful & natural thing women can do ? Today I want to admit something to you : when I started wanting to be pregnant someone asked me “are you going to breastfeed your baby?” & to be fully honest .. i kinda knew what it was but not really, i knew what they meant but also had never seen that in my life ??? Like no one around me has ever breastfeed in front of me, it was never a subject of conversation around me.. idk why but I never REALLY came in front of the subject… is it because we don’t talk about it enough or just a coincidence i had never seen anyone doing it in my entire life ? 💭 when I was pregnant, I was still getting the question & everytime I was always answering “i’ll try but I don’t think it’ll work for me” .. i was saying that because I was scared, my brain couldn’t process the fact that I can create milk & it would come out of my breast ?! It was easier for me to think that my body can create a human than milk 😂 it was just such a weird subject for me !! Then during pregnancy, I was happy to find feminist pages talking about the subject & calling out the fact that everyone is trying to shut it down, my “awkwardness” around the subject made more sense & now that I’m breastfeeding I just really want to be part of the #normalizebreastfeeding movement which is why I share my journey, I often breastfeed in story while doing wtv, I don’t stop myself from breastfeeding in public & sometimes I do photoshoots (actually this photo was not planned, we were doing a photoshoot for my new matching @hoaka_swimwear collection & Wolfie started crying & wanting milk so she pushed my bikini top & started drinking & i was like “yea wtv let’s continue shooting” !! & at the end of the day it fits perfectly the “breastfeeding can be done anywhere & at any moment” 🤱🏼💕

node.text: Have I told you that I had alot of fun today & wanna do this more often ??? 😂 i think i’ve repeated myself too much but girls : I HAD SO MUCH FUN TODAY & I WANT TO DO THIS MORE OFTEN 🤟🏽 comment your country’s flag if you want me to travel to your country to come shoot ✈️ My passion is travel photography, when I first started that it wasn’t even “a thing” yet on IG, there was no like “influenceur” kinda thing, no money in the game or anything like that, it was really JUST for fun & after I was lucky enough to see my passion becoming my work, i got to do this more often & have to admit that after doing the same kinda stuff for years (traveling to get the perfect travel photographies) I felt … uhm idk how to say it, i don’t think the word is “bored” but kinda, well not bored but I needed a new challenge, I needed to do it differently (do you get what i mean ???😂) so that’s when I started doing the Hoaka girls trips, do you girls remember when every month I was doing a giveaway & you could win a fully trip to dreamy destinations with your bestie to come shoot my bikini collections ? 🥺 it was SO NICE, the best concept cause I could finally give back to my community, bring you into my lifestyle, meet you, & everyone had their chance to shoot @hoaka_swimwear so we had more diversity in our travel content BUT THEN ! We all know what happened 1- pregnancy & right after … we know the word (if i write it my post will be messed up: thanks ig!) so I had to stop doing these giveaways ☹️ it’s been 2 years now & i miss it SO MUCH , i’ve only met incredible people through it 🌈 So now that traveling is slowly coming back (crossed fingers for the future) I’m practicing getting used to travel with Wolfie & also practicing photography (cause I used to have the best help but now we need to make the travel team smaller) & i had the idea to shoot local girls at the destinations where I travel to, this way i can practice for when we are actually back to normal & we can restart doing that Hoaka Girls Trips 🌸 shooting with locals is so nice cause I can actually meet the real people from the place I go to & know more about everything ✨ thank you sm @halima.jzl & @tory.arevalo 🇪🇸

node.text: Her first time in Europe 🥺💕 so very happy to be experiencing her first time in Spain 🇪🇸 we currently have absolutely no plans haha We only booked our flights & .. that’s it ! So time to let us know WHAT DO WE ABSOLUUUUTELY NEED TO SEE ? ✨ Since we really wanted to come here but knew we couldn’t rent a car (cause i couldn’t get my international liscence on time) we decided to do a “common transportation trip” which means : we didn’t bring Wolfie’s car seat cause we didn’t want to have a to bring it everywhere so we can only travel by bus or train while we’re here 🚂 I’ve done this kinda trip twice in the past in Italy, after talking to locals, they told me transportation is very similar & it’ll be easy to see the principal only this way … so we’re now trying it ! We have no plans cayse we’ll see if it’s really easy or not & we’ll go day by day in case there is a spot we love too much ✨ we’re just not stressed about life right now, it is vacation time & my Sagittarius self can only be excited about this new adventure 🌈 i thought this way of traveling was going to be over for me when I have Wolfie but actually no, she doesn’t care if we don’t know where we are sleeping tonight, she wouldn’t even know either way 😅 nothing is certain except that every night she’ll have a bed & everyday she’ll eat good european food .. it can’t go wrong (could it ?😂)

node.text: Family tourist day to celebrate our reunion 🐠 Today was my happiest day in a long time (note: I said happiest, cause I’m always very happy but today was extra extra mega happy) ☀️ Since I had Wolfie in my life, I’m the happiest i’ve ever been but I think i can say the same about Christo now, we’ve been away for so long and it made me realize how much he counts for me (& for Wolfie) 🌈 it felt so weird when we saw each other again (those who saw the video will understand haha) it was like we didn’t know each other even tho we spent months together 24/7 & even when he was gone we would facetime every single day for 2 months but… yea the feeling to see each other again was so weird, it was like i had never met him, he felt kinda “not real” for me, maybe it was too beautiful to be true ?? But finally my brain processed it & after only 15 minutes it was like he never left 💕 we’re so happy to be back together, we don’t know for how long but i’ll do my best to never be away for that long again 🥺 we like you @c.r.iscontreras 🥰

node.text:
Matcha & palm trees, all i’m wishing for right now 😋🌴 I can’t stop thinking about going back to Costa Rica soon, I’m too excited (also enjoying my time here at the same time, i’m just happy in general with my life so i’m not rushing haha) 🌈 there is 2 things I really like about Costa Rica that are visible in this pic : 1- I can walk almost anywhere with a bikini, they don’t care it’s “la pura vida” , people are not bothering with things that are not important ! Life is too short to get negative feelings from stupid things that don’t change anything in your life ( for example : most places I’d feel judge to walk in a bikini anywhere but in Costa.. not at all ! & there is so many other things like that.. let me convince you : in the area where I am I could bring my dogs to the restaurant 😍 LIFE GOALS JUST FOR THAT) & the second thing I really love that we can see in this photo is the food ! Since I got here I feel like it tastes so different, the food there is incredible, super natural i’d say, they often cook with what they have in their garden or just around & that’s something I really appreciate the veggies & fruits are so yummy 😋🪴 so, who wants to move with me ? ✈️ 
Oh & another thing i really appreciate there is my friend @daryaseafilms who takes the best photos on earth 🌍

node.text: PINCH ME !!!! After a crazy weekend, today we’ve just had a little reveal event for our next warehouse 💕 YES WE’RE BUILDING OUR OWN GIANT WAREHOUSE & IT’LL BE INCREDIBLE  I STILL CANNOT BELIEVE IT 😭 What does it mean ? More inventory & more launch & more items & just more more 🌈 actually it is already under construction & it’ll be ready in January but I had to keep the secret hihi 🥰 I remember when I started my business, I was 17 & it thought “oh it’ll be nice to have abit of side money while i’m at university” finally 6 years later look at where we are !! People always tell me “look at what you’ve built” “you’re so inspiring for entrepreneurs” , that’s super sweet but honestly if it was just me all alone Hoaka wouldn’t be here ! We’re all the family included in this adventure now, every members of the family is so important to our success (can I call it a success myself ??? Maybe yes just for today haha!!) & not only my family but also all of the Hoaka team, we’ve had girls working with us for up to 4 years , they’ve lived this adventure with us 🦋 & of course I want to mention all of you girls who have been supporting us in any way, by buying a bikini or sharing a giveaway, by posting with Hoaka or only liking our photos, honestly just all the love & support we get from the start is out of this world, thank you for trusting us 🌸 also a big thank you to everyone implicated in this project, there is not enough space here to thank everyone I wish to thank but ILY ALL … so ! Do you like it ?! 😍
